(1, 'Political News', 'Stay informed about the latest developments in politics with our comprehensive political news coverage. From national elections and government policies to international diplomacy and political scandals, we provide in-depth analysis and up-to-date reports on the figures and events shaping the political landscape.', '2024-08-28 17:42:42', '2024-08-28 17:46:05'),
