(4, 'Sports News', 'Dive into the exciting world of sports with our up-to-the-minute sports news. Whether it\'s scores, player transfers, match highlights, or analysis of major sporting events, we cover a wide range of sports including football, basketball, tennis, and more. Stay on top of the action and never miss a moment of the excitement.', '2024-08-28 17:47:20', '2024-08-28 18:14:44'),
