-75.5-184.5q0-109 75.5-184.5t184.5-75.5q109 0 184.5 75.5t75.5 184.5q0 44-14 83t-38 69l252 252-56 56zm-404-280q75 0 127.5-52.5t52.5-127.5q0-75-52.5-127.5t-127.5-52.5q-75 0-127.5 52.5t-52.5 127.5q0 75 52.5 127.5t127.5 52.5z\"></path></svg>&nbsp;<span class=\"google-anno-t\" style=\"border: 0px !important; box-shadow: none !important; display: inline !important; float: none !important; margin: 0px !important; outline: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; text-decoration-line: underline !important; text-decoration-style: dotted !important; color: inherit !important; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; font-style: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">gospel</span></a>&nbsp;singer narrated how her mother nearly aborted her because she was still a student when she got pregnant with her.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">According to Esther Smith, her grandmother’s sister met her mother on her way to abort the pregnancy and sounded the alarm which eventually caused her father to stop her mother.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">“My mother was a school girl when she was pregnant with me. She was going to abort meat Komfo Anokye because she was scared of her father because she was the only child.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">“So, on her way, she met her mother’s sister who asked her where she was going. The woman followed her until she confessed her intentions to her. My father did not also like the idea of giving birth. So the woman reported to my father that my mother was going to abort me and she was stopped.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">“She confessed that she had taken a lot of drugs to help with the abortion but none of them worked,” she narrated on Thursday, August 29.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">The singer disclosed this while she was opening up about her singing talent, noting that singing is an innate talent from birth.</p><div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Esther Smith said after that incident a pastor met her mother and told her she [Esther Smith] was going to become a prominent personality in Ghana.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">“My mother said she met a pastor who told her that the baby she is carrying would grow to become useful to Ghana. So, when God started lifting me, she told me about the story,” she added.</p></div>', 1, 2, '2024-08-30 22:37:02', '2024-09-06 10:44:07', 'thumb_66d22d6e12ba95.48474356.jpg', 'gospel', 0, 'Gospel musician, Esther Smith has shared an emotional yet inspiring story about her birth.'),
(20, '24/25 UCL draw: Cristiano Ronaldo honoured for outstanding goal scoring exploits', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">The award was handed over to the Al-Nassr man by UEFA president Aleksander Ceferin.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Ronaldo, who made his Champions League debut for Manchester United almost two decades ago, scored 140 times in 183 games.His goalscoring cut across Manchester United, Real Madrid and Juventus, winning five Champions league trophies in the process.</p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-left: 21px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://3news.com/sports/football/champions-league-draw-real-madrid-face-liverpool-dortmund-and-ac-milan-in-new-format/\" style=\"color: var(--td_theme_color, #4db2ec); text-decoration: none;\">Champions League draw: Real Madrid face Liverpool, Dortmund, and AC Milan in new format</a></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Ronaldo played in six Uefa Champions League finals, winning five and losing one. Pressed upon to single out his favourite title winning campaign, the former Real Madrid man said:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">“Well, it’s difficult to pick one but we always mention the first one. The first one is the most special one. I remember when I was in Manchester, I won and I scored in the final too; I missed a penalty too, but it was good. I remember that it was so special,” he revealed. Ronaldo enjoyed the moment in 2008 scoring a crucial goal against Chelsea in an exciting final which ended 1-1 after extra-time. Despite missing his kick, the Red Devils eventually won on penalty shootouts to clinch their third and last UEFA Champions League.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">The revamped Champions League draw has concluded with mouthwatering fixtures cutting across.</p>', 1, 4, '2024-08-30 22:39:34', '2024-08-30 22:39:34', 'thumb_66d22e06051413.25522934.jpg', 'football', 0, 'All-time top scorer of the  UEFA Champions League, Cristiano Ronaldo, was honoured by  UEFA with a s'),
(21, 'Napoli sign Romelu Lukaku from Chelsea in £30m deal', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">The move reunites Lukaku, 31, with manager Antonio Conte, who previously managed him during two successful seasons at Inter Milan from 2019 to 2021.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Lukaku rejoined Chelsea in 2021 for a then-club record fee of £97.5 million but spent the last two seasons on loan in Italy, first at Inter and then with Roma.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Under Conte at Inter, Lukaku scored 24 league goals and played a crucial role in their Serie A title win in 2021, which led to Chelsea bringing him back to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://3news.com/sports/football/napoli-sign-romelu-lukaku-from-chelsea-in-30m-deal/#\" class=\"google-anno\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34) !important; text-decoration: none !important; border: 0px !important; box-shadow: none !important; display: inline !important; float: none !important; margin: 0px !important; outline: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; fill: currentcolor !important;\"><svg viewBox=\"100 -1000 840 840\" width=\"calc(15px - 2px)\" height=\"15px\" style=\"color-scheme: initial !important; forced-color-adjust: initial !important; mask: initial !important; math-depth: initial !importan