(36, '2024 Polls: Mahama to submit his nomination forms to EC on Monday', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The forms will be submitted on his behalf by the National Chairman of the NDC, Johnson Asideu Nketia.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">In a post on his Facebook page, Mr Mahama said “My nomination forms as Presidential Candidate of the National Democratic Congress (NDC), with Professor Jane Naana Opoku-Agyemang as Vice Presidential Candidate, will be formally submitted to the Electoral Commission on Monday at 2.00 pm.</span><br></p><p style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing, 1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">“The submission of the forms by our National Chairman, Johnson Asiedu Nketiah, represents a pivotal step in our campaign for change on December 7. We are all in this together, working with Ghanaians to RESET Ghana’s economy and ‘Build the Ghana we want together’.”</p><div><br></div><div data-ad-id=\"409525\" class=\"afw afw-ga afw_ad afwadid-409525  \" style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing, 1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40); text-align: center; float: none; display: none !important;\"><ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-3177501661880531\" data-ad-slot=\"6425443323\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0p