(38, 'Man drugs his wife so over 50 men could rape her more than 200 times', '<p style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing,1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Gisèle Pélicot, 72, testified at the ongoing trial in Avignon, France. Her husband, Dominique Pélicot, 71, is among the 51 men facing rape charges.</p><p style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing,1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">According to reports, Gisèle believed she was attending a routine police interview with Dominique regarding a recent up skirting incident. However, the officer revealed disturbing photographs showing an unconscious Gisèle being raped by another man.</p><p style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing,1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Devastated, Gisèle recounted a seemingly happy marriage shattered by her husband’s betrayal. She revealed overcoming financial and health struggles together, and even forgiving the initial up skirting incident.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: var(--cp-spacing,1.5rem); color: rgb(40, 40, 40); width: 728.703px;